parameters.name: AcceptLanguage
parameters.description:
The language of the response. Valid values:

*   zh: Chinese
*   en: English

parameters.name: Id
parameters.description: The custom ID of the namespace. If you do not specify this parameter, the automatically generated Universally Unique Identifier (UUID) is returned.

parameters.name: Name
parameters.description: The display name of the namespace.

parameters.name: ServiceCount
parameters.description: The maximum number of services that can run in the namespace.
